Goa is the most perfect all-year holiday destination, a place where you can have a vacation of a lifetime. Goa is a lush green paradise edged by wooden foothills of the Sahyadri range on one side and by the Arabian Sea on the other. It's a tiny emerald land on the West Coast of India, with its natural scenic beauty, attractive beaches and temples famous for its architecture, feasts and festivals. Above all, it has hospitable people with a rich cultural milieu making it a perfect spot for an awesome vacation.